subtitleNullable: Perform Text Classification, Summarization in Nepali using this Dataset
descriptionNullable:
This data set contains ~7500 news articles which I had collected from Nepali news Websites. 

The data set has been cleaned and contains fairly balanced train and test set using which you can train and test your classification models, text summarization models in Nepali

The scripts which were used to create the data set can be found [here](https://github.com/goru001/nlp-for-nepali/tree/master/datasets-preparation)
